arch:property.oc:show_val: Brownish soil layer, 10YR5/4 (yellowish brown), representing a short abandonment period or deposition of debris after the construction of the secondary architecture of Phase II. It lies located in the south of the trench, in the exedra apse an sloping up to the north face of the structure, and overlies and seals many of the features there.
